\cf1\insrsid10058183  term for tax-paying provincials, the literal equivalent of Old English }{\i\cf1\insrsid10058183 gafolgelda}{\cf1\insrsid10058183 , ('taxpayer'); one such charter, of about 725 (Birch, }{\i\cf1\insrsid10058183 Cartularium Saxonicum}{
