not entirely, for church dues, first attested in the 920s (Edward and Guthrum 3 = Attenborough,}{\i\cf1\insrsid10058183\charrsid13699272  Laws of the Earliest English Kings}{\cf1\insrsid10058183\charrsid13699272 
, pp. 98-99); and see references under 'Plough', indexed in Attenborough,}{\i\cf1\insrsid10058183\charrsid13699272  Laws of the Earliest English Kings}{\cf1\insrsid10058183\charrsid13699272 , and Robertson, }{\i\cf1\insrsid10058183\charrsid13699272 La
